Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:28.82,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,100)\fad(500,500)}「因为千寻来看我了哦！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:46.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}忠海站和竹原站的开头发音都是「た」（ta）。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为听到了「た」  我还以为到竹原了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匆匆忙忙下车  结果到了一个叫忠海的站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我马上就去坐下一趟电车啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  下一趟要过一小时才来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻你先等着  我去问问妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看有没有人可以开车去接你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  离下一趟电车来还有一小时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去接吧  枫你回玉响咖啡店等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是刚才借的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…妈妈在骑机车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有机车？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是长大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几位是以前关照过你妈妈的骑手俱乐部的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出生的时候  我们大家都来看过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么点点大的小宝宝居然长得这么漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  是因为上年纪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近眼睛变得容易流汗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  想看玉惠以前的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉惠姐以前很帅的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体型虽然小  但是机车骑得很熟练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都已经长得这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来邀请我们说「好久没骑过了  下次的骑行大家一起去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和机车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了  回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经骑得很慢了  还是觉得害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  很开心的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待下次的骑行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信联系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妈妈让我带的土产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  千寻会由我们来好好照料的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼的天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻很喜欢吃章鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也吃吃看  吃吃看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是广岛油菜  我最喜欢吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是因为章鱼很好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是因为枫喵在平常地笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开朗地在生活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  觉得安心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻和枫从小学起就一直在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  枫喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗哟噗哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神真好呢噗哟助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了很多新伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要向小薰她们介绍你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵每天都有拍照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大概是有每天在拍啦  虽然没什么长进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能在竹原见到千寻了  好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:29.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音你太紧张了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪的朋友  我记得是个爱哭鬼吧  薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是个泪腺脆弱的人  还有不要叫我薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得注意别不小心打开她的泪腺开关了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到了  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  多么闪亮的香亲笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要把纪惠亲我给萌死吗  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心乱了阵脚  不妙不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫三次千寻  这次…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呦  没想到能在这里和你相见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是冈崎纪惠  多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塙薰  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是樱田麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去吃什锦烧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照香亲说的  去吃吧去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新品「HOBORO烧」  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  闻起来真香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情地来品尝以战胜夏天的暑气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香亲  很烫的哦  要我帮你吹吹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗  不烫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是用这个吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烫的  要小心吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻是第一次来竹原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那你们待会儿得带她好好四处转转呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  等下去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那个…我想想从哪儿开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  你先吃完再说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们真的叫你小啪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在这里我被叫做小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是  我家姐姐看到小啪的动作后命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边你是怎么叫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵枫喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是刚上小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来玩躲避球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三次千寻同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡枫…枫…枫喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻和我都不擅长交新朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不正好有个合适的去处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}竹原本町大道石阶旁的名胜。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「举地藏」？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说一边许愿一边抱起地藏菩萨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果比想象中的要轻的话  那个愿望就能实现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  毕竟是石头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当情绪下降的时候  果然还是要吃二重烧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在高处吃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能情绪UP！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这风景如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:17.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里是指竹原港方向的竹原冶炼厂的烟囱。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  烟囱那头还能看到海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔和大家一起来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个不错的地方吧  千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜食和美景都没办法提升她的情绪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  现在我情绪很高涨的…说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱  太可爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小家伙是什么啊  软绵绵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.99,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情绪高涨到爆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃猫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃猫大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉真棒  情绪高涨起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样达到最高点吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老姐发信息来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我不敢听  但是内容是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是绝好的探险之日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就无视掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  无视什么的好过分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:02.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}竹原市忠海町的山，被当地人爱称为「黑泷先生」。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  大家一起去黑泷山  让情绪UP吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑泷山？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开车去吗  恐怖的驾驶再临…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路去？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  打起精神出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走去黑泷山…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦  在这种探险的大好日子里才不要开车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起佐代美姐的驾驶这还算是好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这样想了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵  忠海就是我下错车的那一站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很远吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}这之后1小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}2小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐电车不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:27.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}3小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  休息5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里的话就只有一点了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  要吃汽水橡皮糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽水橡皮糖？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是纪惠我亲手做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不吃那种奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝她就好了  千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜呜  谁都不吃我做的汽水橡皮糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  香亲居然来吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪惠亲我的幸福指数一下子就满了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多吃点  吃多少都行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻自己做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻喜欢可爱的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口哨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  还有一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不止一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要继续走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  已经到了哦  登山口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要爬黑泷山啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才刚开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好做准备体操哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备体操2分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  因为到山顶要二三十分钟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又囧又可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手制的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好地方呢  枫喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够和千寻来没来过的地方  真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:19:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵过得很好  很好  真的过得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻  谢谢你为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来泪腺的开关在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现小香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交朋友可真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不擅长交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有被谁搭话的经历吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同班有个对噗哟助…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这孩子叫噗哟助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说这孩子很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她给我看了自制的布娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱  做得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算是朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们也是千寻的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我去试试看和那孩子搭话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能收下这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺摩朗  佩夫洛  喵比利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋啪夫  优汪特  朵莎朵莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  佩夫洛  到我这来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵也拿一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友吧  来交换邮箱地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜  泪腺的开关又…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  纪惠  麻音  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  噗哟助  要再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「下次一定要登上黑泷山的山顶」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家老姐发来了这样可怕的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻  谢谢你过来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那时听说枫喵交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实觉得很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算远隔他乡  时光荏苒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一直是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在那个时候那个地方相遇的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会消逝的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还要和今后相遇的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开的新的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要积极向前看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.25,0:24:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「因为是曾经的回忆」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.86,0:24:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「而且因为是某一天的回忆」
